snippet.title: Interior Worlds - An ambient exploration game where you'll dive into strange, yet familiar spaces!
snippet.description:
Purchase on itch.io https://sodaraptor.itch.io/interior-worlds?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Empty lots. Blackened buildings. Dimly lit hallways.

They all live and breathe just as we do.

Welcome to Interior Worlds; an ambient first person exploration game where you'll dive into strange, yet familiar spaces.

Temporary gaps and portals we cross at some point or another - now yearning for a closer look. A look that can only be seen properly through the lens of an SLR camera.

➡️ More from sodaraptor https://sodaraptor.itch.io/?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
➡️ More low-poly games https://itch.io/games/tag-low-poly?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
